RE New TW ContractCapacity Release System DemoYES I have added you to our RSVP list Original Message From Lokay Michelle Sent Monday March PM To Carrillo Alma Subject FW New TW ContractCapacity Release System Demo Is there still room in the class Thanks Original Message From Trevino Linda Sent Friday February AM To Lohman TK Donoho Lindy Lindberg Lorraine Lokay Michelle Harris Steven Moore Jan Watson Kimberly McConnell Mark Ybarbo Paul Mulligan Amy McEvoy Christine Miller Christopher L Ward Linda Hernandez Bert Minter Tracy Buchanan John Blair Lynn Giambrone Laura Schoolcraft Darrell Hanagriff Richard Cc Dietz Rick Carrillo Alma Licciardo Jeanne Subject New TW ContractCapacity Release System Demo The new TW ContractCapacity Release system is due to be implemented the weekend of March We will be offering trainingdemos of the new system for internal users on the below dates Please contact Alma Carrillo with the date and time you would like to attend Thanks Linda Monday March th Two Sessions pm and pm Thursday March st One Session pm If you have any questions or will be unable to attend one of the above demo sessions please let me know

FW itinerary for grace lynn blair aug travel Cc FYI Original Message From Cynthia Biggs mailto Sent Monday August PM To Carrillo Alma Subject itinerary for grace lynn blair aug travel AGENT MPCB BOOKING REF YHFU BLAIRGRACE LYNN EB ETKT RECEIPT ENRON CORP DATE AUG SERVICE DATE FROM TO DEPART ARRIVE CONTINENTAL AIRLINES AUG HOUSTON TX OMAHA NE P P CO K MON GBUSH INTERCO EPPLEY AIRFIEL TERMINAL C NON STOP RESERVATION CONFIRMED DURATION AIRCRAFT MCDONNELL DOUGLAS MD ALL SERIES SEAT D NO SMOKING CONFIRMED BLAIRGRACE LYN HOTEL AUG REGENCY PARK PLAZA AUG S TH AVENUE OMAHA NE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA TELEPHONE FAX CONFIRMATION QYJYTW SINGLE ROOM RATE ENR USD PER NIGHT GUARANTEE GIVEN ENRON CORP RQST NONSMK KING TO AVOID BILLING CANCEL HOTEL BY PM DAY OF ARRIVAL CONTINENTAL AIRLINES AUG OMAHA NE HOUSTON TX P P CO K TUE EPPLEY AIRFIEL GBUSH INTERCO TERMINAL B SNACK NON STOP RESERVATION CONFIRMED DURATION FLIGHT OPERATED BY EXPRESSJET AIRLINES I AIRCRAFT EMBRAER RJ SEAT B NO SMOKING CONFIRMED BLAIRGRACE LYN THIS IS AN ADVANCE PURCHASE REFUNDABLE FARE CHANGES MAY RESULT IN AN ADDITIONAL COLLECTION YOUR TICKET REFLECTS A NEGOTIATED DISCOUNT FROM THE TAP THE PUBLISHED FARE FOR THIS TICKET IS MISCELLANEOUS DEC HOUSTON TX WED THANK YOU FOR USING THE TAP RESERVATION NUMBERS COUFL BLAIRGRACE LYNN SCR TICKETCOETKT CO FREQUENT FLYER COGH ASSISTANT AVA GARCIA INTL TVLRS CARRY SOS WALLET CARD WENRON ASSISTANCE INFO CALL SOS MEDICAL EMERGENCYIN US CALL SOS MEDICAL EMERGENCYINTL COLLECT THIS IS THE PASSENGER RECEIPT FOR YOUR ELECTRONIC TICKET LEASE CHECKIN WITH PHOTO IDENTIFICATION AND WITH EITHER THIS RECEIPT OR YOUR CONFIRMATION NUMBER YOUR ETKT CONFIRMATION NUMBER IS UFL ALL FARES ARE SUBJECT TO CHANGE UNTIL TICKETEDPURCHASED
